msgid ""
"Examine various fields to see if they contain the search pattern: The "
"pattern вҖңmeetвҖқ would match вҖңkick-off meetingвҖқ. Wildcards вҖң*вҖқ (matches any "
"number of characters) and вҖң?вҖқ (matches any single character) are supported.  "
"For example, the search pattern вҖңmeet*bossвҖқ matches вҖңMeeting with bossвҖқ. The "
"pattern вҖңc?tвҖқ would match вҖңcatвҖқ, вҖңcotвҖқ, and so on."
